== 開發 ==
游戏作者YandereDev名为Alex，是[[美国|美国]][[加州|加州]]的一位[[独立游戏|独立游戏]]开发者，曾在一家游戏公司工作3年。2014年4月1日，YandereDev在[[4chan|4chan]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://twitter.com/YandereDev/status/632366199888678912|title=YandereDev on Twitter|accessdate=2016-04-27|archive-date=2017-03-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170315171349/https://twitter.com/YandereDev/status/632366199888678912|dead-url=no}}</ref>上面公开了病娇模拟器的游戏创意，得到了非常正面的反映，于是开始借鉴[[刺客任務|刺客任務]]系列和校园类游戏的创意，独立开发《病娇模拟器》。最初遊戲完全由YandereDev一人開發，後來很多志願者也加入了開發，提供編劇、配音、3D模型等方面的幫助。<ref name="interview">{{cite web|url=http://gamesnosh.com/gamesnosh-interviews-yanderedev-yandere-simulator/|title=Gamesnosh Interviews – Yanderedev (Yandere Simulator)|publisher=Gamesnosh|accessdate=2016-04-22|archive-date=2016-04-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160420234631/http://gamesnosh.com/gamesnosh-interviews-yanderedev-yandere-simulator/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

遊戲的第一個測試版本於2015年1月公開發佈。目前固定於每月的1號與15號發布新的公開測試版本，並於YandereDev [[Youtube|Youtube]]頻道中介紹新版本中的功能展示。<ref name="meme" />每次更新都會添加一些新元素，例如對情敵下毒、使情敵觸電身亡、使情敵溺亡等。<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.siliconera.com/2015/05/21/how-to-make-a-murder-look-like-suicide-in-yandere-simulator/ | title = How To Make A Murder Look Like Suicide In Yandere Simulator | last = Priestman | first = Chris | date = 2015-05-21 | website = [[Siliconera|Siliconera]] | publisher = [[Curse,_Inc.|Curse, Inc.]] | accessdate = 2016-01-10 | archive-date = 2016-03-13 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160313125411/http://www.siliconera.com/2015/05/21/how-to-make-a-murder-look-like-suicide-in-yandere-simulator/ | dead-url = yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.destructoid.com/yandere-simulator-lets-you-poison-japanese-schoolgirls-293353.phtml | title = Yandere Simulator lets you poison Japanese schoolgirls | last = Hansen | first = Steven | date = 2015-06-05 | website = [[Destructoid|Destructoid]] | publisher = [[ModernMethod|ModernMethod]] | accessdate = 2016-01-10 | archive-date = 2016-01-25 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160125031458/http://www.destructoid.com/yandere-simulator-lets-you-poison-japanese-schoolgirls-293353.phtml | dead-url = no }}</ref>但是作者表示，目前的版本還不能算作「真正的遊戲」，只能算是「放滿玩具的[[沙盒|沙盒]]」。<ref name="interview" />

